videos.description: Bryce Brown comes off the screen and shoots a 3-pointer that takes a couple bounces to go down.
videos.headline: Auburn's Brown gets very lucky bounce

videos.description: Mizzouri's Jordan Barnett makes a sloppy pass and Desean Murray throws it down.
videos.headline: Auburn's Murray makes Mizzouri pay

videos.description: Jared Harper shows great vision and lobs it to Mustapha Heron who throws down the nice jam.
videos.headline: Auburn's Heron gets highlight-reel slam

videos.description: Terrence Phillips gets the loose ball and finds Kassius Robertson in transition and he flies through the air for the one-handed stuff.
videos.headline: Missouri's Robertson soars for slam

videos.description: Jordan Barnett knocks down the corner 3-pointer, then Kassius Robertson comes right back and drains one himself to pull the Tigers within one.
videos.headline: Missouri cuts lead with 3-pointers

videos.description: Mustapha Heron pokes the ball away then dribbles all the way for the breakaway slam.
videos.headline: Heron's feisty defense leads to Auburn slam

videos.description: Jared Harper finds Mustapha Heron who makes a textbook fake and cuts to the basket for the slam.
videos.headline: Heron's fundamentals leads to nice slam
